title: United Kingdom Imports - Optical, Photo & Cinema Graphics & Related Acces.
description: Imports - Optical, Photo & Cinema Graphics & Related Acces. in the United Kingdom decreased to 1382.96 GBP Million in September from 1481.48 GBP Million in August of 2022. Imports - Optical, Photo & Cinema Graphics & Relat in the United Kingdom averaged 893.06 GBP Million from 2000 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 1529.18 GBP Million in October of 2020 and a record low of 515.08 GBP Million in February of 2000.
